## Key constants location

All game tuning lives in `config.py`: costs, sizes, speeds, HP values, spawn rates. Check there before hardcoding numbers.

## How to run the game

```powershell
python main.py
python main.py --no-llm
python main.py --provider mock
python main.py --provider openai
python main.py --renderer pygame
python main.py --renderer pygame --no-llm
```

Default renderer is **Ursina (3D)**. Use `--renderer pygame` for the 2D pygame + `GameEngine` loop (see `main.py`).
